How to run this UVM environment:
1. Open makefile and change the variable UVM_HOME to the directory of your UVM file.
2. Open terminal in this directory and type "make vcs"
3. You can change the variable "tc" for different test cases and variable "vb" to change UVM verbosity, for example "make vcs tc=dense1_smoke vb=UVM_HIGH"
4. After running "make vcs", type "make verdi" to get waveform simulation.
